    <div class="mod comment-m">
        <h2  >大淘小智的影评 &nbsp; &middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/2004909/reviews?cat_id=1002">4篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/5346468/" title="Biohazard: Damnation"><img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s18002077.jpg" alt="Biohazard: Damnation"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="无剧透简评" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/5592175/" class="title">无剧透简评</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
                    <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/2004909/">大淘小智</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;评论:&nbsp;<a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/5346468/">Biohazard: Damnation</a>
                </div>
                <p>前半部分略显沉闷，后面开打了很精彩。尤其是两人联手对抗追踪者的桥段，肌肉感和血腥味十足。
里昂还是通篇耍帅耍酷，ada还是见首不见尾。
画面很细腻，遗憾的是没见到什么新怪物，只有舔食者和追踪者。不过舔食者变成召唤兽了还挺好玩的，上街溜溜霸气十足。<a href="http://movie.douban.com/review/5592175/">(5回应)</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
